headline: 1 Insurance Stock with Exciting Potential and 2 We Ignore
summary: Insurance providers use their expertise in risk assessment to help protect assets while offering consumers peace of mind through comprehensive coverage options. But concerns about claims severity and tightening regulations have tempered enthusiasm, capping the upside for insurance stocks lately - over the past six months, the industry’s flat return has trailed the S&P 500’s 18.6% gain.
